if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為立稅人 我寧願俾錢郵政局蝕住做 都唔想交錢俾差餉/大白象工程<br />\n老實講 政府請人/學資處/房屋署/稅務局都用硬郵政架啦<br />\n如果香港政府唔撚做郵政 咁又交俾邊個私人機構做？ 又點決定俾邊個？<br />\n所以基本上一定唔會執</blockquote><br />\n你夠估唔到條隧道可以判出去管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f096f6f98c54a0272774c005024c94307503e5fc","tid":252151,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點會執<br />\n日日公司一大堆信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府而家話年年蝕大錢同我地呻阿</blockquote><br />\n本地平郵係蝕本的<br />\n寄一封蝕一封<br />\n<br />\n而家收貴左好d"},{"pid":"81287c37f8272b19f5c1f0d716900eabe471348c","tid":252151,"uid":33787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7aac66949248614d651244183ad4db1c32698bdc","tid":252151,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:52:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d8456051c7e077887c37404a3638309cd952612","tid":252151,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:01:45.000Z","msg":"其實我開post係因為見到民協反對石硤尾郵局終止服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但網上搵唔到料有無附近巴打知咩事"},{"pid":"927ad0c43d00b75306c84d6e887fe9788dca6c1c","tid":252151,"uid":64607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點會執<br />\n日日公司一大堆信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府而家話年年蝕大錢同我地呻阿</blockquote><br />\n本地平郵係蝕本的<br />\n寄一封蝕一封<br />\n<br />\n而家收貴左好d</blockquote><br />\n根本上普通信件真係無錢賺，人力、運輸成本計番開，1.7賺得你乜，<br />\n香港寄信空郵去外國都係3.7，3.7真係平盡全球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而速遞就賺好多</blockquote><br />\n空郵佢地租人飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid